These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, vegafina
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, teacher
1. the mechanic is in an even position##4
2. the teacher is the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Cigar   | vegafina | blend |
| Job     | teacher    | mechanic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, scientific
1. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee        |
| Movie-Genre      | zombie  | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, house
House: victorian, wooden
1. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | house    | ambient |
| House   | victorian | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, september
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| Birthday       | april | september    |

