.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, august
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Birthday   | august | december   |
| Sport         | skiing | volleyball |

